Jacuzzi Use Policy

The use of the jacuzzi is subject to the following strict rules and conditions. By accessing the jacuzzi, you agree to comply with these guidelines. Any breach of these rules may result in expulsion from the bathing area without refund.

Minors’ Access Restriction Access to the jacuzzi is strictly reserved for individuals aged 18 and over. Minors are not permitted to use the jacuzzi, even under adult supervision.

Consumption of Food and Beverages

Prohibition of Food Consumption: Eating in or around the jacuzzi area is strictly prohibited.
Alcoholic and Other Beverages Prohibition: The consumption of beverages, including alcoholic drinks, is strictly forbidden in the jacuzzi. No containers, glasses, or bottles may be brought into or near the jacuzzi.
Smoking Prohibition: Smoking, including electronic cigarettes, is strictly prohibited in or around the jacuzzi area.
Hygiene and Appropriate Attire

All users must shower before entering the jacuzzi.
Only proper swimwear is allowed. City clothing or other attire is not permitted in the jacuzzi.
The use of cosmetics, oils, lotions, or sunscreen is prohibited before entering the water.
Safety and Behavior

No Diving: The jacuzzi is not designed for diving. Jumping or diving is strictly prohibited.
No Running or Playing in the Jacuzzi Area: The jacuzzi area must remain calm and secure for all users. Playing or running is not allowed.
Use of Electronic Devices: Electronic devices (phones, speakers, etc.) are not allowed in or near the jacuzzi to prevent the risk of electric shock.
Maximum Capacity Respect The jacuzzi's maximum capacity must be strictly observed. In the event of overcrowding, excess users will be asked to leave the area.

Prohibition of Dangerous Objects No glass, sharp objects, or other dangerous items are allowed in or around the jacuzzi.

Medical Conditions

Any person suffering from health issues such as heart disease, high blood pressure, or skin infections should avoid using the jacuzzi.
Pregnant women are strongly advised against using the jacuzzi.
In the event of non-compliance with these conditions, management reserves the right to ask violators to leave the area immediately.
